Title: Minimizing total weighted completion time in a proportionate flow shop  
Author: Natalia Shakhlevich Han Hoogeveen Michael Pinedo 
Keyword: Key Words and Phrases: flow shop scheduling, weighted completion time.  
Note: 1980 Mathematics Subject Classification (1991):  
Address: Surganov Street 6, 220012 Minsk, Belarus  P.O. Box 513, 5600 MB Eindhoven, The Netherlands  New York, NY 10027  
